title: Big Brother Naija: 5 things that happened on day 25 of reality show
text: Check them out below; 1. Housemates discovered via Biggie 's 'riot act' that they had not only lost this week's wager, they had also lost their Payporte wardrobe shopping. The housemates were warned against any form of wastage. 2. TBoss said that she is the house for the politics and not to entertain. She explained that has never been into entertainment and joined the house to prove something to herself. 3. Bisola discussed her first sexual experience and says she heard her hymen pop in her ear.
